Title: azure_status: Monitor Azure Status
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1668692793
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0b1

It's now possible to monitor Azure Status from
https://azure.status.microsoft/en-us/status in Checkmk. Since this
site is publicly available, no authentication is required for this
monitoring.

One new check has been added, azure_status. To monitor Azure Status
you have to configure the related special agent Microsoft Azure
Status.

